text: Vittangi SK is a sports club in Vittangi in Sweden. It was established in 1959. The women's soccer team played in the Swedish top division in 1982. ==References== ==Other websites== *Vittangi SK Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Athletics clubs in Sweden Category:Gymnastics Category:1959 establishments in Europe Category:Ski clubs in Sweden Category:1950s establishments in Sweden
